1. State Transitions
- RECEIVED → Initial QC
- PROCESSING → Active Analysis
- SEQUENCED → Data Generation
- COMPLETED → Final QC Review

2. Quality Control Gates
- Entry criteria for each stage
- Required QC metrics per transition
- Validation rules for progression
- Rollback handling for failed QC

